        "title": {
          "english": "Expressing 'I want to pay'"
        },
        "text": "To say 'I want to pay', you use بَدّي أَدْفَع (beddi adfa'). بَدّي means 'I want' and أَدْفَع means 'to pay'.",
        "examples": [
